        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer762484129" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15922456204255650628">I have always been fascinated with Vincent Van Gogh&apos;s art and of the man himself. Starry Night is my favorite painting. Irving Stone allows us a peek at Van Gogh the person and how the events of his life shaped the genius of his painting. Stone uses his pen as a brush to paint his portrait of Van Gogh and helped me to better understand the man behind the paintings.</span>
  <span id="freeText15922456204255650628" style="display:none">I have always been fascinated with Vincent Van Gogh's art and of the man himself. Starry Night is my favorite painting. Irving Stone allows us a peek at Van Gogh the person and how the events of his life shaped the genius of his painting. Stone uses his pen as a brush to paint his portrait of Van Gogh and helped me to better understand the man behind the paintings.</span>
