<span id="freeTextContainer14504826995718255893">Irving Stone has been criticised for being populist, but I really enjoyed this imaginative retelling of Van Gogh&apos;s life story. It inspired me to search out his paintings in London&apos;s galleries, and you can&apos;t want for more than that in a biography of an artist.</span>
  <span id="freeText14504826995718255893" style="display:none">Irving Stone has been criticised for being populist, but I really enjoyed this imaginative retelling of Van Gogh's life story. It inspired me to search out his paintings in London's galleries, and you can't want for more than that in a biography of an artist.</span>
